reviewText: This 3 film set released by full moon studios has one true witchcraft movie, a complelation of 3 short witch movies and a movie about a cyborg cop that was just weird. You get Birth Rite the movie that is about a 18yr old girl who learns of her destiny of witchcraft. Next is Possessed which the complilation of 3 short stories. Last is The Occultist which is a weird movie about a cyborg cop.
